"Olga has a great gift for filming with her close team in such a way that we often got carried away by the spontaneous atmosphere and naturally let her into our privacy, thanks to which I talked about topics quite confidential. She and her husband, cameraman Jan malíř, have become part of our family. We originally wanted to release the film in 2019, when I celebrated my life's Jubilee. But because I had a lovely summer with my family, I wanted us to shoot as long as possible. Well, and since there were a lot of me everywhere in 2019, my wish was that it be released to cinemas in the spring of next year. This documentary is a thank you to my supporters and all those who supported and accompanied me in my profession, " says Karel Gott himself.
